@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_gnecgp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (0.46 - wp.abs((v1 + 0.80 + v2 + 0.72)))
    tmp = v1
    v0 = v2
    tmp = wp.exp(tmp)
    v2 = v1
    tmp = wp.sin(((v1 + 0.88 / v0 + 0.22) - (tmp + 0.38 + v2 + 0.67)))
    data[tid] = v0
